accurate</li>\n<li>Using <span class=\"caps\">CCTV</span> recording equipment in and around our premises for security&nbsp;purposes</li>\n</ul>\n"},"relationships":{"paragraph_type":{"data":null,"links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/text-block/2f24c43f-c8c9-4406-84d6-d412f005bf61/relationships/paragraph_type?resourceVersion=id%3A495249"}}}}},{"type":"headline","id":"94754fe7-fe15-4ecd-87ee-5afbcfad7638","links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/headline/94754fe7-fe15-4ecd-87ee-5afbcfad7638?resourceVersion=id%3A495250"}},"attributes":{"resourceVersion":495250,"published":true,"created":"2020-07-29T11:07:03+00:00","parent_field_name":"page_slices","title":"Special categories of personal information","hierarchy":"h2"},"relationships":{"paragraph_type":{"data":null,"links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/headline/94754fe7-fe15-4ecd-87ee-5afbcfad7638/relationships/paragraph_type?resourceVersion=id%3A495250"}}}}},{"type":"text-block","id":"b4dec5a8-c5b3-44e8-b5e7-b1c5cb09b467","links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/text-block/b4dec5a8-c5b3-44e8-b5e7-b1c5cb09b467?resourceVersion=id%3A495251"}},"attributes":{"published":true,"created":"2020-07-29T11:07:46+00:00","parent_field_name":"page_slices","wysiwygEditor":"<p>Data protection law recognises certain “special categories” of personal information, which include information revealing racial or ethnic origin, political opinions, religious or philosophical beliefs, trade union membership, genetic information, biometric information for uniquely identifying a person, information concerning health, and information concerning a person’s sex life or sexual orientation.<br><br>\n<br><br>\nThese special categories are considered particularly sensitive and so we will only collect and use this information where you have given us your explicit consent. For example, you may choose to tell us about your health condition before attending one of ou