ms for example something we think you’d be happy for us to do like contact you when you have actively shown an interest in our activities or&nbsp;services</li>\n<li>Contract – fulfilment of a contract e.g. subscribing to <span class=\"caps\">BFI</span> Player or becoming a <span class=\"caps\">BFI</span>&nbsp;member</li>\n<li>Legal obligation – where we have to use data as prescribed by&nbsp;law</li>\n<li>Vital interests – protecting your health and personal&nbsp;safety</li>\n</ul>\n"},"relationships":{"paragraph_type":{"data":null,"links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/text-block/5f12f326-63af-47c8-b6a7-2d03659e788d/relationships/paragraph_type?resourceVersion=id%3A495253"}}}}},{"type":"headline","id":"adb72d93-efd9-4886-bfa3-1d055470ddeb","links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/headline/adb72d93-efd9-4886-bfa3-1d055470ddeb?resourceVersion=id%3A495254"}},"attributes":{"resourceVersion":495254,"published":true,"created":"2020-07-29T11:35:23+00:00","parent_field_name":"page_slices","title":"Sharing of personal data","hierarchy":"h2"},"relationships":{"paragraph_type":{"data":null,"links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/headline/adb72d93-efd9-4886-bfa3-1d055470ddeb/relationships/paragraph_type?resourceVersion=id%3A495254"}}}}},{"type":"text-block","id":"ef633e64-943a-4f7b-bf1e-2aaff2fabd09","links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/text-block/ef633e64-943a-4f7b-bf1e-2aaff2fabd09?resourceVersion=id%3A495255"}},"attributes":{"published":true,"created":"2020-07-29T11:35:34+00:00","parent_field_name":"page_slices","wysiwygEditor":"<p>We only share your personal data with third parties where we have a legal basis for doing so, such as with your consent or the fulfilment of a contract. For example, to invite you to an event and administer payments. We will never sell your personal&nbsp;information.</p>\n"},"relationships":{"paragraph_type":{"data":null,"links":{"self":{"href":"https:/