\n<br><br>\nYou can then ask us to do the following with the personal information we hold about&nbsp;you:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>If it is incorrect, you can ask for it to be updated – your right to&nbsp;rectification</li>\n<li>Restrict or object to it being processed at all or in a specific way — your right to restrict, right to object and right related to automated decision&nbsp;making</li>\n<li>Ask for it to be deleted — your right to erasure, sometimes called the right to be&nbsp;forgotten</li>\n<li>Ask for a digital copy of it – your right to digital&nbsp;portability</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Many of the rights listed above are limited to certain defined circumstances and we may not always be able to comply with your request. We will tell you if this is the case.<br><br>\n<br><br>\nFor more information on your rights in your personal information, please see the <a href=\"https://ico.org.uk/for-organisations/guide-to-data-protection/guide-to-the-general-data-protection-regulation-gdpr/individual-rights/\"><span class=\"caps\">ICO</span> guidance</a>.</p>\n"},"relationships":{"paragraph_type":{"data":null,"links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/text-block/83487e50-448c-4e84-a783-86db3f934c84/relationships/paragraph_type?resourceVersion=id%3A495265"}}}}},{"type":"headline","id":"e1e90d36-37b6-49f6-95df-10413c9fb2c3","links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/headline/e1e90d36-37b6-49f6-95df-10413c9fb2c3?resourceVersion=id%3A495266"}},"attributes":{"resourceVersion":495266,"published":true,"created":"2020-07-29T14:02:54+00:00","parent_field_name":"page_slices","title":"Changes to this policy","hierarchy":"h2"},"relationships":{"paragraph_type":{"data":null,"links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/api/slice/headline/e1e90d36-37b6-49f6-95df-10413c9fb2c3/relationships/paragraph_type?resourceVersion=id%3A495266"}}}}},{"type":"text-block","id":"1707b5ec-a6a5-4571-a89b-e942df104edc","links":{"self":{"href":"https://core-cms.bfi.org.uk/